my lover and now my eternal life partner. You have brought the light into my eyes and have opened your heart to forgive me of my past wrongs. Your kind heart has always shown everyone including myself kindness and love, I only thank you daily for bringing that into my own heart and blessing my life with another precious daughter. I can only hope that she grows in her father's ways and learns greatly of his teachings. I love you Eli, now and forever. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6>Amazons of the Northern Lands</a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://www.amazonsunite.i-p.com">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.3 b4<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  